    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.03 + wp.sin((tmp + 0.55 * v1 + 0.10)))
    v1 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.01 + v0 + 0.03)) + (v2 / wp.exp(tmp + 0.95)))
    v1 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.63 / v0 + 0.48)) - ((v2 + 0.93 - v0 + 0.67) * (v2 + 0.64 - tmp + 0.79)))
    tmp = 0.83
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.abs(v0 + 0.45) + v2))
    v1 = v0
    v1 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.40 - v1 + 0.96)) * 0.43)
    data[tid] = v0
